NAPLES, Fla. - Participate in a live chat with Naples Daily News journalists and area gridiron fans during Week 8 of high school football action in Southwest Florida. 
Here are Friday night's football games: Barron Collier 13, Golden Gate 0, halftime Community School 26, Evangelical Christian 0, 2nd First Baptist 44, Landmark Christian 0 Marco Island Academy 7, Southwest Florida Christian 0, 1st Moore Haven 30, St. John Neumann 0, 2nd Naples 7, Palmetto Ridge 0, 2nd South Fort Myers 14, Riverdale 7, 2nd Immokalee 9, Mariner 0, 2nd Fort Myers 34, Estero 0, 2nd 
Share your photos with us: Each week fans can submit their photos for a chance to win a large pizza & T-shirt from Il Primo Pizza and Wings. Post game pics to Instagram or Twitter and use #NDNPrepZone for a chance to win. A winner will be selected every Tuesday.
